topic: Companies Workflow Series ("IT Companies explorative search")

goals.1: Identify the BGP for obtaining number of employees of a company and other relevant numerical attributes
goals.2: Identify the BGP to retrieve all companies owned by a company
goals.3: Is there some company that owns companies in other countries?
goals.4: Companies have different 'legal forms', compare the number of companies divided in different legal forms
goals.5: Analyze the number of employees  and other relevant numeric attributes
goals.5.1: What are the top-10 companies for a given attribute?
goals.5.2: For which companies is defined some form of income or market capitalization or total assets? What is the min, max, and average in each category and country?
goals.5.3: Which business in each country owns more businesses in other countries?

name: e5a4ae57ad

search_workflow.query: SELECT COUNT(*) WHERE { ?p wdt:P17 wd:Q16 . ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453 . }

1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?pr ?name WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453 ; ?pr ?o. ?pr sc:name ?name . FILTER(isNumeric(?o)) }

SELECT ?name ?employees ?revenues ?net_profit ?market_cap ?tot_assets WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453. ?p wdt:P1128 ?employees; wdt:P2139 ?revenues; wdt:P2295 ?net_profit; wdt:P2226 ?market_cap; wdt:P2403 ?tot_assets. ?p sc:name ?name . } LIMIT 20
output: S.P. Korolev Rocket and Space Corporation Energia

2.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?pr ?name WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453. ?p ?pr ?o. ?pr sc:name ?name . FILTER (!isLiteral(?o)). FILTER (REGEX(?name,".*wn.*")) } ORDER BY (?name) LIMIT 50
SELECT ?company (count(DISTINCT ?o) AS ?companies_owned) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453. ?p wdt:P1830 ?o. ?p sc:name ?company . } GROUP BY ?p ?company ORDER BY DESC (?companies_owned) LIMIT 50

3.query: ASK WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P17 ?c; wdt:P1830 ?o. ?o wdt:P17 ?own_c. FILTER(?c != ?own_c). }

SELECT ?company (count(DISTINCT ?o) AS ?companies_owned) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P17 ?c; wdt:P1830 ?o. ?o wdt:P17 ?own_c. FILTER(?c != ?own_c). ?p sc:name ?company . } GROUP BY ?p ?company ORDER BY DESC (?companies_owned) LIMIT 50

4.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?pr ?name WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453. ?p ?pr ?o. ?pr sc:name ?name . FILTER (REGEX(?name,".*egal.*")) } LIMIT 50
SELECT DISTINCT ?legal_form (COUNT(DISTINCT ?p) AS ?companies) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P1454 ?o. ?o sc:name ?legal_form . } GROUP BY ?legal_form ORDER BY DESC (?companies) LIMIT 100
output: A natural person doing business according to the Trade Licensing Act not registered in the Commercial Register

5.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?pr ?name WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453 ; ?pr ?o. ?pr sc:name ?name . FILTER(isNumeric(?o)) }
SELECT ?name ?employees WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P1128 ?employees. ?p sc:name ?name . FILTER (isNumeric(?employees)) } ORDER BY DESC (?employees) LIMIT 10
SELECT ?name ?revenues WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P2139 ?revenues. ?p sc:name ?name . } ORDER BY DESC (?revenues) LIMIT 10

SELECT DISTINCT ?country (min(?revenues) AS ?min) (max(?revenues) AS ?max) (avg(?revenues) AS ?avg) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P2139 ?revenues; wdt:P17 ?c. ?c sc:name ?country . FILTER (isNumeric(?revenues)) } GROUP BY ?c ?country ORDER BY DESC (?avg) LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT ?country (min(?net) AS ?min) (max(?net) AS ?max) (avg(?net) AS ?avg) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P2295 ?net; wdt:P17 ?c. ?c sc:name ?country . FILTER (isNumeric(?net)) } GROUP BY ?c ?country ORDER BY DESC (?avg) LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT ?country (min(?op_income) AS ?min) (max(?op_income) AS ?max) (avg(?op_income) AS ?avg) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P3362 ?op_income; wdt:P17 ?c. ?c sc:name ?country . FILTER (isNumeric(?op_income)) } GROUP BY ?c ?country ORDER BY DESC (?avg) LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT ?country (min(?value) AS ?min) (max(?value) AS ?max) (avg(?value) AS ?avg) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P8340 ?value; wdt:P17 ?c. ?c sc:name ?country . FILTER (isNumeric(?value)) } GROUP BY ?c ?country ORDER BY DESC (?avg) LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT ?country (min(?debt) AS ?min) (max(?debt) AS ?max) (avg(?debt) AS ?avg) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P2133 ?debt; wdt:P17 ?c. ?c sc:name ?country . FILTER (isNumeric(?debt)) } GROUP BY ?c ?country ORDER BY DESC (?avg) LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT ?country (min(?cap) AS ?min) (max(?cap) AS ?max) (avg(?cap) AS ?avg) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P2226 ?cap; wdt:P17 ?c. ?c sc:name ?country . FILTER (isNumeric(?cap)) } GROUP BY ?c ?country ORDER BY DESC (?avg) LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT ?country (min(?assets) AS ?min) (max(?assets) AS ?max) (avg(?assets) AS ?avg) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P2403 ?assets; wdt:P17 ?c. ?c sc:name ?country . FILTER (isNumeric(?assets)) } GROUP BY ?c ?country ORDER BY DESC (?avg) LIMIT 20

SELECT ?company ?country (COUNT(DISTINCT ?o) AS ?companies_owned) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P17 ?c; wdt:P1830 ?o. ?o wdt:P17 ?own_c. FILTER(?c != ?own_c). ?p sc:name ?company . ?c sc:name ?country . } GROUP BY ?p ?company ?c ?country ORDER BY DESC (?companies_owned) LIMIT 10

SELECT ?country (max(?companies_owned) AS ?max_owned) WHERE{ { SELECT ?p ?company ?country (COUNT(DISTINCT ?o) AS ?companies_owned) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P17 ?c; wdt:P1830 ?o. ?o wdt:P17 ?own_c. FILTER(?c != ?own_c). ?p sc:name ?company . ?c sc:name ?country . } GROUP BY ?p ?company ?c ?country } } GROUP BY ?c ?country ORDER BY DESC (?max_owned) LIMIT 10

SELECT ?country ?company1 ?max_owned{ { SELECT ?country (max(?companies_owned) AS ?max_owned) WHERE{ { SELECT ?p ?company ?country (COUNT(DISTINCT ?o) AS ?companies_owned) WHERE { ?p wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P17 ?c; wdt:P1830 ?o. ?o wdt:P17 ?own_c. FILTER(?c != ?own_c). ?p sc:name ?company . ?c sc:name ?country . } GROUP BY ?p ?company ?c ?country } } GROUP BY ?c ?country ORDER BY DESC (?max_owned) } { SELECT ?p1 ?company1 ?country1 (COUNT(DISTINCT ?o1) AS ?inside_companies_owned) WHERE { ?p1 wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453; wdt:P17 ?c1; wdt:P1830 ?o1. ?o1 wdt:P17 ?own_c1. FILTER(?c1 != ?own_c1). ?p1 sc:name ?company1 . ?c1 sc:name ?country1 . } GROUP BY ?p1 ?company1 ?c1 ?country1 } FILTER (?inside_companies_owned = ?max_owned && ?country1 = ?country) } ORDER BY DESC (?max_owned) LIMIT 50
